---
import Main from "../layouts/main.astro";

---


<Main>
    <section class="heading-csr md:py-40 relative bg-[#00000090]">
        <div class="md:w-4/5 mx-auto px-10 md:px-0 md:flex justify-between">

            <div class="md:w-3/5 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold text-white uppercase">Hope for Humanity</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-300 leading-8 py-3">Give a helping hand to those in need</p>
            </div>
        </div>
  
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 md:py-20">
      <div class="md:w-4/5 mx-auto">
        <div class="w-4/5 mx-auto">
          <h3 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 text-center uppercase">DAP Humanity</h3>
          
          <p class="text-justify text-xl">For my social initiatives, I firmly believe that serving the people goes beyond political responsibilities. We are committed to making a positive impact on the communities we represent and promoting sustainable development throughout Rivers State and beyond. Through our Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) initiatives, we strive to address critical social and environmental challenges, uplift disadvantaged groups, and foster a brighter future for all Nigerians.</p>

        </div>
                
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-20 my-20">
          <h3 class="w-full mb-12 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 text-center uppercase">Touch Points</h3>
        
          <div class="w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]">
            <div class="w-full h-[300px] flex justify-center items-center mt-8 bg-csr-education overflow-hidden relative rounded-lg">
              <img src="/images/education-icon.png" alt="" class="">
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl py-4 font-semibold uppercase">Education for Empowerment</p>
            <p class="text-base">We understand that education is the cornerstone of progress and empowerment. Our CSR programs aim to improve access to quality education by building schools, providing scholarships, and supporting educational infrastructure development. We believe that by investing in education, we can unlock the potential of young minds and equip them with the tools needed to shape a better Nigeria.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]">
            <div class="w-full h-[300px] flex justify-center items-center mt-8 bg-csr-women overflow-hidden relative rounded-lg">
              <img src="/images/women-icon.png" alt="" class="">
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl py-4 font-semibold uppercase">Empowering Women</p>
            <p class="text-base">We recognize the vital role women play in driving progress and development. Our CSR initiatives promote gender equality, women's empowerment, and youth development through skills training programs, mentorship opportunities, and entrepreneurship support. We believe in fostering an inclusive society where everyone has an equal chance to thrive.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]">
            <div class="w-full h-[300px] flex justify-center items-center mt-8 bg-csr-health overflow-hidden relative rounded-lg">
              <img src="/images/medical-icon.png" alt="" class="">
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl py-4 font-semibold uppercase">Healthcare Initiatives</p>
            <p class="text-base">Accessible and quality healthcare is a fundamental right. We are dedicated to enhancing healthcare services and facilities in underserved areas. Our CSR efforts focus on constructing medical centers, organizing health camps, and supporting healthcare professionals to ensure that basic medical needs are met, and communities receive the care they deserve.
              </p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]">
            <div class="w-full h-[300px] flex justify-center items-center mt-8 bg-csr-community overflow-hidden relative rounded-lg">
              <img src="/images/community-icon.png" alt="" class="">
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl py-4 font-semibold uppercase">Community-Driven</p>
            <p class="text-base">EngagementWe believe in the power of community engagement and collaboration. Our CSR efforts involve actively engaging with local communities, understanding their unique needs, and working together to implement impactful solutions. We encourage civic participation, promote cultural activities, and support community-driven development projects to foster a sense of belonging and pride.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>          
          <h3 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 text-center uppercase">OUR IMPACT</h3>

          <div class="flex py-8 border-y border-y-brandred border-y-1">

              <div class="w-full">
                <p class="text-6xl text-center">N5M+</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-center uppercase tracking-wider">Donations</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full">
                <p class="text-6xl text-center">20+</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-center uppercase tracking-wider">volunteers</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full">
                <p class="text-6xl text-center">10+</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-center uppercase tracking-wider">Communities Impacted</p>
              </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-x-8 my-20">
          
            <div class="w-1/2 flex gap-x-8">
              <div class="w-1/2 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/women-csr.jpg" alt="" class="rounded-lg">
              </div>
              <div class="w-1/2 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/education-csr.jpg" alt="" class="rounded-lg">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-1/2">
              <div class="">
                
                  <div class="bg-csr-video mx-auto h-[400px] flex justify-center items-center bg-[var(--brandred)] rounded-lg">
                      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nt_2Qj4ajuQ&t=63s" target="_blank" title="Watch video" class="h-[50px] transition hover:h-[65px] hover:transition duration-300">
                          <img src="images/video-icon.png" alt="" class="h-full">
                      </a>
                      
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
      </div>

      
    </section>

    <section class="pb-10 md:pb-10 relative">
      <div class="md:w-3/5 mx-auto">     

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black text-center uppercase">Need Assistance?</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 my-8">
              
              <input type="text" class="form-input w-[calc(50%-1rem)] my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50" placeholder="First Name">
              <input type="text" class="form-input w-[calc(50%-1rem)] my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50" placeholder="Last Name">
              <input type="text" class="form-input w-[calc(50%-1rem)] my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50" placeholder="Phone Number">
              
              <input type="text" class="form-input w-[calc(50%-1rem)] my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50" placeholder="Email Address">
              
              <input type="text" class="form-input w-full my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50" placeholder="Email Address">

              <textarea name="" class="form-textarea w-full h-[200px] my-3 py-4 text-lg rounded-md border-brandred shadow-sm focus:border-red-300 focus:ring focus:ring-red-200 focus:ring-opacity-50">Message</textarea>

              <div class="flex justify-center w-full my-4">
        <button class="bg-brandred text-lg text-white font-semibold md:px-12 md:py-2 rounded uppercase hover:bg-transparent hover:text-brandred hover:ring-brandred hover:ring-1 hover:transition">Send</button>
      </div>
                  
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>







    <section class="py-10 md:py-40 mb-[1px] dap-podcast">
        <div class="md:w-4/5 mx-auto">
            <div class="w-1/2">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brandred uppercase">Listen Now</h3>
                <h2 class="text-4xl text-brandred font-bold uppercase">Diary of Dakuku</h2>
                <div class="flex justify-between__ gap-x-8 mt-8">
                    <a href="#" class="text-base hover:font-semibold">
                        <img src="/images/spotify-icon.png" alt="" class="inline h-[40px]">
                        <span>Spotify</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-base hover:font-semibold">
                        <img src="/images/Podcasts_iOS.png" alt="" class="inline h-[40px]">
                        <span>Apple Podcast</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-base hover:font-semibold">
                        <img src="/images/Google_Podcasts_icon.png" alt="" class="inline h-[40px]">
                        <span>Google Podcast</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Main>